	  New interface structures for non invasive access to core
	  functionality.

2002-05-07 22:30  pgregory

	* render/: texturemap.cpp, texturemap.h: Move texture handling back
	  into the core where it belongs, other modules can access it via
	  the new interfaces. This decision is due to the nature of the
	  texture cacheing mechanism which is/will be very core specific.

