	  revisions and comments added.

2002-03-07 13:08  pgregory

	* libcodegenvm/vmoutput.cpp: Fix long time annoying bug in shader
	  VM. Multiple light sources would cause odd artifacts, due to
	  illuminance construct in VM bailing out completely if one
	  lightsource didn't contribute, thus subsequent lightsources were
	  missed.

