2001-05-21 23:28  tshead

	* ChangeLog, Makefile.am, aqsis/Makefile.am, aqsis/aqsis.cpp,
	  libaqsistypes/.cvsignore, libaqsistypes/Makefile.am,
	  libaqsistypes/color.cpp, libaqsistypes/vector4d.cpp,
